    pl "The only one bold around here is YOU! And what in god's name are you even wearing?!" with sshake


translate English day2_ed15f842:


    lz2 "What? This? I just woke up and forgot to change..."


translate English day2_6881d541:


    lz2 "Oopsie doopsie! I'm such a klutz."


