    nar "Glancing down at herself, she spins around on the spot, posing like a model in a magazine."


translate English day2_1e59814d:


    nar "Her outfit doesn't leave much to the imagination. Do all city women dress like this...?" with sshake


translate English day2_f89b413e:


    pl "Do you usually forget to get dressed? Go back and change already!!!"


translate English day2_1e21648d:


    lz2 "So, honest opinion. How do I look?"


translate English day2_92cb086f:


    pl "...Good enough."


translate English day2_7f77d24a:


    lz2 "Yeah?"


translate English day2_cf95f048:


    nar "She's absolutely pulling my leg here." with sshake


