    lz2 "We're neighbors, aren't we? I had to say hello."


translate English day2_5d22d7df:


    pl "Well, for your information, I wasn't out late because I wanted to be. I went to take a look around and got lost... "


translate English day2_389b57ba:


    pl "The temple is massive."


translate English day2_6ca01ac5:


    lz2 "You must've had a great time. Don't worry, it'll all fall into place soon enough!"


translate English day2_2f3344c7:


    lz2 "Just don't be late tonight, 'kay? I wanna visit later!"


translate English day2_cfdf4877:


    lz2 "Oh! Also, could you tell everyone I'm gonna be late?"


translate English day2_f610bf64:


    pl "Why?"


translate English day2_3097efd3:


