    pl "Well... fine. But if you don't put some clothes on, you're gonna catch a cold!"


translate English day2_9a338542:


    lz2 "Hahaha!"


translate English day2_acccdf69:


    lz2 "Hilarious as always!"


translate English day2_76b2fe88_2:


