translate English day2_0e67be86:


    nar "Her high-pitched laughter follows me as I head to the gathering spot for our department."


translate English day2_22734111:


    nar "The Cleanup Department, located in the most dimly lit corner of the building, always seems bathed in shadows. The closer I get, the more humid it feels."


translate English day2_db3483cc:


    pl "Good morning."


translate English day2_92a87a7e:


    nar "I croak, my voice oddly deep. The tension in my shoulders is even affecting my throat."


translate English day2_b791477d:


    nar "A chorus of muffled voices returns the greeting..."


translate English day2_31257bed:


    nar "...Although it's hard for me to tell where they're coming from since no one looks up."


translate English day2_15b41b62:


    nar "Those who reflexively glance my way quickly lose interest."


translate English day2_f734c8fa:


    pl "Morning, Maya!"


translate English day2_6135b5e5:


    nar "Well, I am the new guy here. I find myself calling out to the only familiar face in the room."


translate English day2_0372d7f2:


    my "Oh! [na2]... Good morning. Did you make it back alright last night?"


translate English day2_fe4ba181:


    nar "With only her face turned in my direction, her ladylike posture makes her look almost like a peony. She's adorable."


translate English day2_d31823cb:


    pl "I told you, I'm pretty good at finding my way around. How did you sleep? I found the pillows here are kinda lumpy and uncomfortable."


translate English day2_fc1c6a3b:


    lz1 "Hey, you. Did you come here by yourself?"


translate English day2_02b6502c:


    pl "Oh, you're here, too?"


translate English day2_356d182d:


    lz1 "Just answer the question! Where's that girl? She still in her room?"


translate English day2_44d0bd4c:


    pl "Ah, Blondie said she'd be late."


translate English day2_038b24fd:


    lz1 "Pretending to be sick to get out of work again, huh?"


translate English day2_90ea1769:


    pl "She said something about feeling bloated and sick sometimes."


translate English day2_f1674024:


    lz1 "Excuses! That's what she ALWAYS says to get out of morning meetings. You should know better! Besides, I'M the one who's gonna get in trouble for it!"


translate English day2_02585da9:


    pl "First of all, it's way too early in the morning for this..."


translate English day2_9f9d95a9:


    nar "For some reason, the Cleanup Department meets earlier than the others."


translate English day2_92f640bf:


    nar "With a high proportion of uneducated lower-class youngsters in the Cleanup crew,"


translate English day2_9b8bfd35:


    nar "it's necessary for the bishop to teach them the fundamentals."


translate English day2_720bf26f:


    nar "The younger priests arrive before the workday starts for class, with the more experienced and older priests filtering in sometime later."


translate English day2_24a27237:


    my "I had a proper education, you know..."


translate English day2_674b1a64:


    lz1 "For some reason, the temple seems to attract mannerless country bumpkins with no common sense"


translate English day2_8f3ae15a:


    lz1 " like moths to the flame--and it's normal folks like us who pay for it. What a nuisance!"


translate English day2_eb1e660c:


    pl "..."


translate English day2_dc30c0ac:


    nar "A chill instantly fills the room. It's probably from the way I shut my mouth halfway through her diatribe, though I had no intention of doing so."


translate English day2_d7f22d4c:


    nar "Maya shoots me an uneasy glance. {w}I have a hunch she thinks I'm offended."


translate English day2_684abba8:


    my "U-Um... She didn't mean you, of course, [na2]..."


translate English day2_705d6661:


    lz1 "Did I stutter?! I meant exactly what I said!!! For crying out loud...!"


translate English day2_02c1a4cc:


    "\n Suddenly, I see a tall shadow outside the window and hear the sharp click of heels."


translate English day2_c6002c0f:


    "The sound instantly dispells the suffocating silence."


translate English day2_e3212589:


    "The door bangs open, accompanied by a cheerful \"Good morning!,\" {w}and a chorus of replies echoes through the room, louder than when I arrived."


translate English day2_82eae8cc:


    "As they step inside, memories of what happened the night before sucker punch me in the brain."


translate English day2_54a453ff:


    et "Unable to return their greeting with my mouth hanging open, all I can do is stare, my eyes following their every move."


translate English day2_424425c0:


