translate English day2_8e0bc061:


    hk_q "{color=#000}{size=0}{k=-0}Don't forget, all your wonderful bodies are on loan from God.{/k}{/size}{/color}{fast}{nw}"


translate English day2_07963355:


    hk_qns "So be sure to take good care of them so you don't get sick!"


translate English day2_49904541:


    nar "Their long, loose skirt, fluttering around around their legs with the slightest movement, seems in direct contrast by their white hair tied back in a tight bun."


translate English day2_cab14121:


    nar "Haku Eckaran, the Cleanup Department's Bishop. I swear I saw them in the forest yesterday, but..."


translate English day2_24ba88cb:


    pl "Huh... They're very different from what I expected."


translate English day2_2a66dd27:


    lz1 "Shhh! Be quiet!"


translate English day2_4e4cb7e9:


    nar "Her warning comes a moment too late. {w}The bishop's eyes meet mine, which have been glued to them since they walked through the door."


translate English day2_c3a717ff:


    nar "Compared to yesterday, they seem far more relaxed."


translate English day2_5d325834:


    hk "Ah, yes. Perfect timing!"


translate English day2_fc6f58f6:


    hk "I have some great news. We have a new brother and sister who will be joining our department from today on!"


translate English day2_c22a9f6a:


    hk "And this is our first proper face-to-face meeting..."


translate English day2_d8c53481:


    extend " isn't it?~"


translate English day2_a45b508e:


    hk "My apologies about yesterday. I had urgent matters to attend to."


translate English day2_e5c3ed28:


    nar "They speak in an oddly low voice, as if trying to hide their naturally more high-pitched one."


translate English day2_871eeca7:


    nar "Their laid-back drawl combined with their uniquely odd pronunciation leaves me struggling to understand them."


translate English day2_d382904b:


    nar "Meanwhile, their eyes continuously dart around the classroom with sharp, quick movements."


translate English day2_9d830829:


    hk "Now then, you two! Go on and introduce yourselves!"


translate English day2_88556e1e:


    nar "I cough quietly, trying to shake off the awkwardness of having everyone's eyes on me."


translate English day2_3893880a:


    nar "It'd be great if I could speak without my voice cracking."


translate English day2_52a82477:


    pl "My name's [na2]. I come from an area fairly far from here. With this being my first time here at both the temple and the capital itself, I'm still pretty lost."


translate English day2_9f8ae01c:


    pl "I heard I might be transferred to a different department once my probation is over, but for now, it's nice to meet all of you."


translate English day2_8fca27ad:


    nar "The bishop, who'd been listening with an expression of bewilderment on their face, belatedly claps in response. Did I say something strange?"


translate English day2_daff3be6:


    nar "It doesn't bother me, "


translate English day2_ed43ad37:


    extend "but I'm worried about Maya."


translate English day2_4e969821:


    nar "I glance over to see her frozen in fear. Her entire body is stiff as a board and her eyes are glued to her fingertips."


translate English day2_90cb1b9a:


    lz1 "AHEM!"


translate English day2_8ea2afe3:


    my "E-Eep..."


translate English day2_4a9144d7:


    nar "Her sister claps her hands together, breaking the silence before it can deepen any further."


translate English day2_b5a93371:


    nar "Maya looks so miserable, legs shaking with fear and unable to look up from the floor, that I can't bring myself to watch."


translate English day2_793b2a9b:


    nar "She's like a newborn baby animal."


translate English day2_276adbcd:


    my "I'm M-Maya Elbeth... N-N-Nice to meet you..."


translate English day2_a078fd3a:


    hk "Well, well! An Elbeth girl, huh? How adorable!"


translate English day2_7251594d:


    nar "Unlike with my intro, there is some scattered applause, though it comes off more like mockery than a genuinely warm welcome."


translate English day2_f212340e:


    nar "I have a feeling it's probably directed more at me than her."


translate English day2_f95512a5:


    my "Ngh..."


translate English day2_0c3f69a1:


    lz1 "Crap! Why is the disposal team looking this way?"


translate English day2_6c305791:


    nar "For someone who usually stares people down with overbearing confidence, she's had her gaze focused at her feet this whole time."


translate English day2_3ef33c76:


    nar "And I can hear her mumbling and swearing under her breath."


translate English day2_6fb1a6b7:


    nar "Seemingly unaware, the beaming bishop opens their mouth once more."


translate English day2_013a829b:


    nar "It's this lack of awareness that makes everyone around them suffer."


translate English day2_822ad5c0:


    hk "I wish the two of you the best of luck! Go get 'em!"


translate English day2_bca33fc8:


    nar "The bishop then immediately dives into a history lesson."


translate English day2_bf3158ff:


    nar "They talk about the prophet, stigmata, the rotting sea, and the barren wastelands unfit for human life."


translate English day2_4cf78f40:


    nar "I'm pretty proud of myself for not dozing off halfway through."


translate English day2_bb84b4e3:


    hk "What we do for others, we do for the lord, our God. He watches over us, always..."


translate English day2_1be2ed3b:


    sc "It's about time for the meeting to start, Your Excellency."


translate English day2_633f3ba1:


    nar "Securett steps in, suddenly interrupting the bishops edifying sermon, {w}albeit seemingly without a hint of malice."


translate English day2_6263942c:


    nar "His voice isn't loud or commanding, but it's enough to instantly change the atmosphere in the room. {w}The bishop's eyes suddenly widen in surprise."


translate English day2_786bba9b:


    hk "Well, well! My, my! There I go, losing track of time again..."


translate English day2_c299de7e:


    hk "Now then, everyone! Make sure to help your two new colleagues out if you see them having trouble!"


translate English day2_4e359285:


    hk "And you two, do what you're told, okay? Feel free to ask if you have any questions."


translate English day2_80599bcf:


    hk "Speaking of which... DO you have any questions?"


translate English day2_6d5ca8ad:


    nar "The uncomfortable silence between us is once again thankfully broken."


translate English day2_3dac0161:


    sc "Doesn't seem like they do."


translate English day2_93f1ddcd:


    hk "In that case, be sure to love one another, today, always, and forever."


translate English day2_42ddb05a:


    nar "And with that, the bishop gracefully departs, followed closely by Securett, cloaked in a black veil."


translate English day2_c57dca07:


    nar "Even the way the bishop moves is bizarre."


translate English day2_5cb9d8ea:


    nar "The detachment between their joints makes them look like a strung marionette--as if they hold no control over their own limbs."


translate English day2_bdf876aa:


    nar "It's almost as if they might fall at any moment, needing someone by their side at all times to catch them."


translate English day2_217e53b1:


    nar "And almost as proof of this,"


translate English day2_7ed117ef:


    nar "Securett's eyes remain glued to the bishop's back as they leave together."


translate English day2_81cbb456:


    nar "The door closes and once their footsteps fade into the distance, the noise level within the Cleanup Department quickly returns to normal."


translate English day2_1cef9179:


    pl "The bishop seems pretty laid-back."


translate English day2_28927980:


    my "The stories I've heard paint her very...*differently*."


translate English day2_0ee7f499:


    my "Though the way she talks, she sounds like a princess reigning over a field of flowers."


translate English day2_2ada81ad:


    pl "Wait... You're saying that person is a woman?"


translate English day2_3b454a9c:


    my "I think so..."


translate English day2_4e7e8ba3:


    lz1 "You don't often see a bishop with white hair. It's kinda funny."


translate English day2_6879cada:


    lz1 "But do you know what's funnier? I heard she was transferred here from a higher position of power."


translate English day2_5e374498:


    pl "I'm not following. What do you mean?"


translate English day2_738011f9:


    nar "Her eyes light up as I take the bait, her former awkward boredom completely gone."


translate English day2_79d7a155:


    nar "Is gossiping about others really that fun for her?"


translate English day2_59070cb7:


    lz1 "She's the daughter of a cardinal. That's how she gets away doing whatever she wants."


translate English day2_13d90e52:


    lz1 "We should feel blessed being dumped in this god forsaken department to clean up corpses, right?"


translate English day2_a570dee2:


    lz1 "By the way, You better not go spreading any of this around."


translate English day2_ce7e07be:


    lz1 "And especially not in front of that annoying jerk."


translate English day2_6898d3ef:


    my "You mean Securett?"


translate English day2_5c5b02ee:


    lz1 "There's no need to remember that sleazebag's name!"


translate English day2_1ca809fd:


    my "Mngh..."


translate English day2_b7768118:


    nar "After finally getting her voice back, poor Maya once again firmly clamps her mouth shut."


translate English day2_5fce3ace:


    nar "...I can't tell if they get along or not."


translate English day2_c4bf4d3e:


    nar "Knowing she'll just keep picking on Maya, I speak up in an attempt at diverting her attention."


translate English day2_b5b25e9f:


    pl "Oh, why's that?"


translate English day2_eb8ddfaa:


    lz1 "Securett hates the bishop more than anyone else on the disposal team."


translate English day2_2b3ceba2:


    lz1 "Just hearing her name causes his face to wrinkle up in disgust."


translate English day2_f5b74625:


    pl "You're serious? But they just left together."


translate English day2_164d21bb:


    lz1 "He's her assistant for the time being."


translate English day2_dee8bc16:


    lz1 "His resume's not strong enough for anything but a temp position, though he's aiming for her spot."


translate English day2_82c16101:


    lz1 "All you need to know is it's a huge mess. The sooner this rat's nest goes under, the better, in my opinion..."


translate English day2_84f35ab9:


    pl "What do you have against him?"


translate English day2_4c11b666:


    lz1 "Look, just drop it already! You have eyes, you can do your own snooping on your own time!"


translate English day2_dc47ca1d:


    pl "You'll get wrinkles if you keep scowling like that..."


translate English day2_434e2e91:


    lz1 "Ugh! For crying out loud!" with sshake


translate English day2_08705a40:


    nar "Looks like she's on the warpath again..."


translate English day2_bdd52dea:


    nar "Conversation between two women passing by floats in and the chairwoman freezes in place."


translate English day2_681ea27b:


    nar "I wish I could work with my sister, too!"


translate English day2_8c2131c4:


    nar "...Do you even have one?"


translate English day2_f40bf585:


    nar "...Hahaha!"


translate English day2_eba1ae34:


    nar "It's the type of conversation we probably wouldn't have heard if we weren't paying attention. But just that snippet is enough to turn her face bright red."


translate English day2_7f9bbf2a:


    nar "She's clearly run out of patience."


translate English day2_00f91b1e:


    nar "Unable to hold back any longer, she vents her anger out on the defenseless chair next to her before turning her death glare directly on us."


