    nar "After shouting at us, she stomps out, a look of fiendish rage clear on her face."


translate English day2_c9976b49:


    nar "It doesn't bother me, but to leave Maya behind like that... She hangs her head, depressed."


translate English day2_9a1e385b:


    my "I don't know what to do today..."


