    my "My sisters aren't around... and even Cue left first thing in the morning..."


translate English day2_4baf893c:


    pl "Don't worry about it, Maya. We already have a basic understanding of what needs done, right? We can just do what we did yesterday."


translate English day2_0f92f889:


    pl "And if we somehow mess up, no one will blame us. {w}They'll blame our seniors who abandoned us without proper instructions!"


translate English day2_cac543b7:


    my "I g-guess you're right... Ugh... When I'm alone, I start to panic."


translate English day2_dd32f92f:


    nar "My attempt at smoothing over the situation seems to work, as her anxiety starts to slowly melt away. {w}And I didn't accidentally say the wrong thing this time."


